high_descs: Turn left and walk to the blue coffee machine.
Pick up the mug from the coffee machine.
Turn right and walk to the fridge.
Chill the mug in the fridge and then pick the mug up from the fridge.
Turn left and walk to the cabinet below the red toaster.
Place the mug in the cabinet below the red toaster.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled mug in the cabinet below the red toaster.

high_descs: Move to the left, and find the coffee maker on the right side.
Pick up the mug from the coffee maker.
Carry the mug and move a few steps to the right to find the fridge.
Place the mug inside the fridge and shut the door. Open the door and take the mug out, then shut the door.
Carry the mug and take a few steps to the left.
Place the mug in the right cabinet under the counter and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Chill a mug and place it in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn left and face the coffee machine on the counter.
Pick up the mug from the coffee machine.
Go to the fridge on the right.
Open the fridge and put the coffee mug inside for a minute and then take it out.
Open the cupboard and put the mug inside.
anns.task_desc: Chill the mug and put it in the cupboard.
